longBusinessSummary: Qiiwi Games AB (publ) develops and publishes games for mobile platforms in Sweden. The company focuses on developing mobile games for casual gamers within the trivia, match-3, and word/puzzle genres. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Alingsås, Sweden.
